00:21:14,649 --> 00:21:16,859
- Marlin! Nemo!
- Dory!

373
00:21:16,985 --> 00:21:18,065
No, no, no. Not again! Not again!

374
00:21:18,195 --> 00:21:19,735
Let's take her inside
and see how she does.

375
00:21:22,699 --> 00:21:23,369
Dory! Dory!

